The following program is a systemized way of creating items for adveture games. 
It is meant to be used as a helper tool in world building and creating of volume
as games require a lot of items, this program thorugh randomization makes it easier to do that.

Simply write the file path where you want your items to be stored and save them.
When you want to see all ypour amazing items click the display button and inspect them.

REMEMBER TO TURN ON YOUR SOUND, THE PROGRAM CONTAINS SOUND EFFECTS FOR A BETTER USER EXPERIENCE.

Thank you for purchasing our software.
